*Postali* smo najbolji prijatelji. (We became the best friends.)
Oni su *postali* to što jesu zahvaljujući svojoj volji. (They became what they are due to their will.)
Ukoliko ne budeš pažljiv, *postaćeš* žrtva prevare. (If you're not careful, you will become a victim of fraud.)
Njihovi problemi su *postali* toliko teški da ih je bilo teško rešiti. (Their problems became so difficult that it was hard to solve them.)
Nakon burne diskusije, odluka je *postala* jasna. (After a heated discussion, the decision became clear.)